===Sulawesi and Sangihe Islands===

Four [[peninsula]]s dominate the shape of [[Sulawesi]] island (formerly known as Celebes). The central part is a high mountainous area, but mostly non-volcanic. Active volcanoes are found in the northern peninsula and continuously stretch to the north to [[Sangihe Islands]]. The Sangihe Islands mark the border with the [[Philippines]].

