==Major eruptions==
Below is a list of selected major eruptions of volcanoes in Indonesia, sorted chronologically by the starting date of the eruption. Only eruptions with scale 3 or above on [[Volcanic Explosivity Index|VEI]] are given with known sources and fatalities, except if smaller scale eruptions resulted some fatalities.

